h3. Summary

Document mentioned background reindex does not reindex Comments, Work Logs and Change History but there is no information about project reindex.
 - [JIRA Indexing FAQ|https://confluence.atlassian.com/jirakb/jira-indexing-faq-776654790.html]
{quote}4. Configuration changes never require Comments, Work Logs and Change History to be reindexed and so a background reindex does not reindex these entries. (Some of these may be reindexed for some issues to ensure correctness of the index for issues that are updated otherwise while the reindex is running).
{quote}

h3. Suggestion

According to the source code, Single Project Re-indexing reindex Issue and Work Logs. Suggest to update what data are included to project reindex.
